What is important is to legalise pagan beliefs which was banned by Buddhist Kings(Sihaleses).It is sad laws like those are used against Hela. It’s like reading a news about someone practicing animal sacrifice will have you banned and lose your job.

Anybody who dares to talk about Hela (what is formally called Dharma Vachakgaru) should be lauded and supported.

Noble vanaspathy is a Universal religion provides peaceful coexistence and happiness to everyone.
